                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Financial Disconnect</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                            <li>"Invoices get held up because techs forget to log materials."</li>
                            <li>"We have to write off a lot of time on big projects."</li>
                            <li>"We've struggled with cash flow because of slow billing."</li>
                            <li>"Features we need on our current system are behind paywalls."</li>
